{"tid":1116032,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"Ed Sheeran〈Thinking Out Loud〉抄襲疑雲再擴大！法官說「太多地方相似","createTime":"2019-04-19T15:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T19:04:07.000Z","uid":60117,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ea492bde61631eaaf911569f57676b2ddc2fcb","tid":1116032,"uid":60117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:33:36.000Z","msg":"俗話說樹大招風，Ed Sheeran早已是全球巨星等級的歌手，卻也因為他的名氣過大，被指控許多音樂創作其實是抄襲前人的作品，幾乎哪首紅，哪首就被放大檢視，也時常被網友諷刺為靠複製貼上而紅的歌手。如今風波顯然尚未結束，近日美國聯邦地區法院法官Louis Stanton駁回Ed Sheeran要求撤銷抄襲Marvin Gaye名曲的訴訟，決定要讓Ed Sheeran負擔起這個責任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEd Sheeran於2014年發行的超紅金曲〈Thinking Out Loud〉，被控訴抄襲已故靈魂樂歌手Marvin Gaye的經典名曲〈Let's Get It On〉，法官最後認定兩首歌曲「有太多相似的地方，無論從音樂創作的元素上來看，或是在旋律、和聲的使用上，實在無法同意Ed Sheeran撤銷訴訟的要求。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陪審團在觀看上面那支影片後，也驚訝表示兩首歌曲原來可以如此天衣無縫地結合在一起。影片為幾年前Ed Sheeran表演〈Thinking Out Loud〉時，現場發揮小心思，偷偷在歌曲裡融合〈Let&rsquo;s Get It On〉的副歌（04:30秒處），台下歌迷還興奮地尖叫，現在這支影片看起來格外諷刺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「雖然兩首歌曲並不完全相同，但我們仍然認為〈Thinking Out Loud〉的確有挪用〈Let's Get It On〉音樂元素的責任。」〈Let&rsquo;s Get It On〉的共同創作者Ed Townsend，他的法定繼承人同時也是訴訟發起人，更表示認同，希望幫助已故的Townsend討回應有的智慧財產權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這也不是第一次Ed Sheeran遭受如此控告。感人金曲〈Photograph〉被第七季《X FACTOR》冠軍Matt Cardle指控抄襲其歌曲〈Amazing〉；紅透半邊天的神曲〈Shape Of You〉也被發現與90年代女團TLC的歌曲〈No Scrubs〉有「異曲同工之妙」；Ed Sheeran為Tim McGraw和Faith Hill譜寫的〈The Rest Of Our Life〉被控告抄襲了Jasmine Rae的〈When I Found You〉，如此雪片般的控訴層出不窮，也讓人懷疑Ed Sheeran真正的創作實力。<br />\n<br />\nEd Sheeran目前尚未出面回應，但法官的判決已下，只等雙方最終的協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/column/showbiz-0-4614-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Ftc%2Fcolumn%2Fshowbiz-0-4614-1.html&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLA%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=626abb86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/tc/column/showbiz-0-4614-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"dfc99380acdbaa29e88ab5d5e2f41f6a7ea156e3","tid":1116032,"uid":60117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34fff1bd523016469aeba409318d3c9b7451143","tid":1116032,"uid":60117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382b1253a1622653038bccaaedfc5a7ea53a7c13","tid":1116032,"uid":60117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5324723d02848bcba162caaa62233be0b6edbe18","tid":1116032,"uid":60117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f27da39767000fe193a0e9f0eeff60369bc788","tid":1116032,"uid":60117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff139aaa303a0d34885df24dc01d79b8c85ddb6c","tid":1116032,"uid":60117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d3a3d267774ad5e6b5750af9cae09d411512af","tid":1116032,"uid":60117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b32268056ea5d4fd68e4d17f72454e7b7dcf6f3","tid":1116032,"uid":24457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:38:26.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野"},{"pid":"82ad14f2bc9ae340ee08549e90d71aab859e0866","tid":1116032,"uid":60117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7accb99e038febce7be52a946fbc85d8a9b87b92","tid":1116032,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0